{"tid":2095162,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下點樣encrypt dual boot系統","createTime":"2020-07-05T08:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:36:21.000Z","uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0df76ae3b7065ee7ac9fea8dba8e9cc02f3249b3","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"用緊Windows+Ubuntu, 想問下點樣encrypt依兩個系統先安全同方便？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用Veracrypt encrypt Windows？ Ubuntu又點encrypt好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66758280e18146aa096bdf16842b439f0893d3b","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"luks ?"},{"pid":"1c8566629f36c40525e8458225b43ac42e91c6ae","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d66758280e18146aa096bdf16842b439f0893d3b","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"luks ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"都得既，不過覺得用luks開個encrypted area再裝ubuntu唔方便姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bb4c06fd0056165a9ae183b48e3d5d1a5ac3d8","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c8566629f36c40525e8458225b43ac42e91c6ae","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d66758280e18146aa096bdf16842b439f0893d3b","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"luks ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"都得既，不過覺得用luks開個encrypted area再裝ubuntu唔方便姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁安全呢樣野一定係雙向<br />\n鎖，冇咁方便但安全 D<br />\n唔鎖，方便 D 但冇咁安全<br />\n一係裝 ubuntu 時 tick 埋 encrypt home directory"},{"pid":"7b20d0259b84b5cf5843fe9decf61270e0ea4ffd","tid":2095162,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T22:26:03.000Z","msg":"印像中ubuntu/mint個啲installer都係tick個 checkbox就幫你做哂luks encryption<br />\nbtw<br />\nencrypt partition 可以shrink<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">sudo cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/sda2 cryptdisk\nresize2fs -p /dev/CryptVolumeGroup/Home 208G</code></pre><br />\n/home partition可以後期先encrypt<br />\n只有/root一定要安裝系統個陣揀做encrypt, 如果唔係裝完後期就無辦法做encryption, 變咗唔係 full system encryption ((其實聽講好似有計嘅, 唔知會唔會courrpt<br />\n有錯屌大力啲"},{"pid":"ddb7e54b149df8860ec0b66218ab2338f6f560a4","tid":2095162,"uid":49803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T23:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3934c17557e2a27b948fa1feacea04a3c097bb20","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9bb4c06fd0056165a9ae183b48e3d5d1a5ac3d8","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c8566629f36c40525e8458225b43ac42e91c6ae","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d66758280e18146aa096bdf16842b439f0893d3b","tid":2095162,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"luks ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"都得既，不過覺得用luks開個encrypted area再裝ubuntu唔方便姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁安全呢樣野一定係雙向<br />\n鎖，冇咁方便但安全 D<br />\n唔鎖，方便 D 但冇咁安全<br />\n一係裝 ubuntu 時 tick 埋 encrypt home directory"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"感謝清！！ 用luks同veracrypt分別encrypt左ubuntu同windows了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7714199341be580630ee4a60f0ca28a693470753","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b20d0259b84b5cf5843fe9decf61270e0ea4ffd","tid":2095162,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T22:26:03.000Z","msg":"印像中ubuntu/mint個啲installer都係tick個 checkbox就幫你做哂luks encryption<br />\nbtw<br />\nencrypt partition 可以shrink<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">sudo cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/sda2 cryptdisk\nresize2fs -p /dev/CryptVolumeGroup/Home 208G</code></pre><br />\n/home partition可以後期先encrypt<br />\n只有/root一定要安裝系統個陣揀做encrypt, 如果唔係裝完後期就無辦法做encryption, 變咗唔係 full system encryption ((其實聽講好似有計嘅, 唔知會唔會courrpt<br />\n有錯屌大力啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"感謝清！！ 用luks encrypt左ubuntu了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似後期就無辦法做encryption了，我就encrypt完先裝ubuntu<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd41d599581660fea6c432b709e8279ad366fd0","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb7e54b149df8860ec0b66218ab2338f6f560a4","tid":2095162,"uid":49803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T23:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"感謝清！！ 我跟住你個網打command，用luks encrypt左ubuntu了，依家dual boot冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055733ea86a18cccb522cacf11ccab13d640ae55","tid":2095162,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd41d599581660fea6c432b709e8279ad366fd0","tid":2095162,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb7e54b149df8860ec0b66218ab2338f6f560a4","tid":2095162,"uid":49803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T23:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim